'''The Art of Underworld''' is an article by [[Joe Corroney]] that appeared in the online supplement to [[Star Wars Insider 89|''Star Wars Insider'' 89]]. The article explores the creative process behind Corroney's work for ''[[Underworld: A Galaxy of Scum and Villainy]]''.

